    "body": "background:\r\n\r\nwe have a mature IOS project for which we are trying to use reactNative only for some parts of the application. so we already have built an extensive Model layer natively and we intend to keep it native. we also have plans to migrate this Model layer to Swift Value Types. \r\n\r\nideally we would like to be able to export our new Model layer as swift value types to js.\r\n\r\nQuestion:\r\n\r\nthe guide covers how we should export a class with `RCT_EXTERN_MODULE` and `RCT_EXTERN_METHOD`. can we do the same with a swift struct?"
